{"tid":2417004,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"關注百老匯院線擬改用人臉辨識量度體溫","createTime":"2021-02-21T13:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T04:29:45.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc4b69bbfc0e2e6a6971c06727c8b5296055f8d","tid":2417004,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"戲院雖然已在二月十八日重開，然而政府對於戲院重開增加了不少規範。當中除了量度體溫外，更需要確保觀眾使用「安心出行」描掃二維碼或留下個人資料。有關戲院嘗試找方法減省其他程序，不過部分做法並不可取。<br />\n<br />\n上圖所見，便是「講。鏟。片」讀者今天在元朗My Cinema Yoho Mall入口所攝，可以看到在戲院的其中一個向公眾展示的幕屏，竟然是以人臉辨識來顯示其溫度，更顯示了日期與時間。如斯方式，難免令人擔心是否有關畫面會被錄取，以及有沒有違反《個人資料（私隱）條例》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/80932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F80932&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=cf9c8fb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/80932</a>"},{"pid":"dc09f7ea39448d8618598801223dce0b4790f9da","tid":2417004,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7f3012f42cbdeeb551b3580edd9f06b36a4d53","tid":2417004,"uid":315645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:29:45.000Z","msg":"???"}]}